          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/436_step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and roughly chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and roughly chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks (save some leaves for garnish)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
